------------------BUILD INSTRUCTIONS---------------

1. Linux 12 or higher
2. sudo apt-get install subversion build-essential libxml2 libxml2-dev freeglut3 freeglut3-dev libglew-dev libsoil1 libsoil-dev
3. svn co https://artrix.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ artrix
3. cd to newly created directory artrix (that has the makefile), and type sudo make
4. go for a cup of coffee, ahen you return, ./artrix to launch



